snippet.title: Matthew Goode, Annabelle Wallis, Roman Griffin Davis "Silent Night" LA Special Screening Red Carpet
snippet.description:
Subscribe! http://bit.ly/mrSda2
Broll footage: Matthew Goode, Director/Writer Camille Griffin, Annabelle Wallis, Roman Griffin Davis, Hardy Griffin Davis, Gilby Griffin Davis on the red carpet at the special screening of AMC+/RLJE Films' darkly comedic drama/horror film "Silent Night" held at Neuehouse Hollywood in Los Angeles, California USA on November 30, 2021

00:00 intro
00:06 Matthew Goode, Director/ Writer Camille Griffin, Annabelle Wallis
00:20 Roman Griffin Davis, Hardy Griffin Davis, Gilby Griffin Davis
01:46 Producer Celine Rattray, RLJE Films Mark Ward
